      <p class="description">Forest use data measure human use of forests, especially the boundaries of areas allocated for a certain land use through concessions, licenses, permits, titles, management units, etc.</p>

      <ul class="sources">
        <li data-slug="logging" class="first">
          <div class="source_header">
            <strong>Logging</strong>
            <i class="expand_arrow"></i>
