              <dl class="sources_row even">
                <dt>Source data</dt>
                <dd>Generally based on a combination of government documents, satellite imagery, and GPS data.<span class="hidden">For information on country-specific concessions data please refer to the Data page.</span></dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="sources_row">
